    "actor_description": "The noise in my head drops out. My attention narrows until there's only the next step, and my body keeps meeting it without hesitation. I'm not forcing anything-decisions arrive already made, corrections happen before they become mistakes, and time stops feeling like time. There's a clean, quiet momentum to it, like I'm being pulled forward along a track I can finally trust.",
    "description_text": "{actor} settles into a steady rhythm-minimal wasted motion, no visible searching, no second-guessing. Their focus holds without strain: eyes tracking precisely, hands moving with practiced economy, breathing even. They look absorbed in a way that's hard to interrupt, as if the task has become the whole room.",
